---
// Terms of Service Page
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | EduLaluan">
  <Header />

  <main class="min-h-screen bg-surface">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-8">Last updated: March 20, 2026</p>

        <div class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground mb-4">
            By accessing and using EduLaluan, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement.
            If you do not agree to abide by these terms, please do not use this service.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">2. Description of Service</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground mb-4">
            EduLaluan is an education resource navigator that helps Malaysian students and families discover scholarships,
            courses, vocational training, and financial aid programs. The service provides:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-foreground mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li>Education resource database</li>
            <li>Scholarship and financial aid information</li>
            <li>Community contribution platform</li>
            <li>User accounts with gamification features</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">3. User Accounts</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground mb-4">
            To access certain features of the service, you must create an account. You agree to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-foreground mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li>Provide accurate and complete registration information</li>
            <li>Maintain the security of your account credentials</li>
            <li>Notify us immediately of any unauthorized use</li>
            <li>Be responsible for all activities under your account</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">4. User Contributions</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground mb-4">
            Users may submit education resources, financial aid programs, and other content. By submitting content, you:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-foreground mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li>Represent that you have the right to submit such content</li>
            <li>Grant EduLaluan a license to use, display, and distribute the content</li>
            <li>Agree that content will be reviewed by moderators</li>
            <li>Understand that inappropriate content will be removed</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">5. Prohibited Conduct</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground mb-4">You agree not to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-foreground mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li>Submit false, misleading, or harmful information</li>
            <li>Use the service for any illegal purpose</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to the service</li>
            <li>Interfere with or disrupt the service</li>
            <li>Harass, abuse, or harm other users</li>
            <li>Submit spam or repetitive content</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">6. Gamification System</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground mb-4">
            EduLaluan includes a points and badges system to reward contributions. You agree that:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-foreground mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li>Points and badges are awarded at EduLaluan's discretion</li>
            <li>Abuse of the system may result in point removal or account suspension</li>
            <li>Weekly submission limits apply based on user tier</li>
            <li>EduLaluan reserves the right to modify the gamification system</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground mb-4">
            The EduLaluan service, including its design, features, and content, is protected by copyright and intellectual property laws.
            You may not copy, modify, or distribute any part of the service without permission.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">8. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground mb-4">
            THE SERVICE IS PROVIDED "AS IS" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED.
            EDULALUAN DOES NOT WARRANT THAT THE SERVICE WILL BE UNINTERRUPTED, SECURE, OR ERROR-FREE.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground mb-4">
            EDULALUAN SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, OR CONSEQUENTIAL DAMAGES ARISING FROM
            YOUR USE OF THE SERVICE, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO LOSS OF DATA, LOSS OF PROFITS, OR BUSINESS INTERRUPTION.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">10. Modifications to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground mb-4">
            We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the service after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">11. Termination</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground mb-4">
            We may terminate or suspend your account at any time for violation of these terms or for any other reason at our discretion.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">12. Governing Law</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground mb-4">
            These terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of Malaysia.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">13. Contact Information</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground mb-4">
            For questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:
            <br />
            Email: <a href="mailto:support@edulaluan.my" class="text-primary hover:underline">support@edulaluan.my</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            By using EduLaluan, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
